    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you look at the environmental side of it, though, is there really much of a debate on whether it's a good move for hitting climate goals, or is the whole thing basically just a necessary step for urban sustainability?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
